low-fat alternative to typically high-fat Memorial Day menus. ; Photo, Tuck 
mozzarella and mushrooms between two ground turkey patties on the grill this 
Memorial Day. ; Photo, Chicken, sweet red peppers and broccoli spears are 
grilled and served as a salad for the holiday. 
