TEACHERS -- LOS ANGELES; TEACHERS -- LABOR RELATIONS; TEACHERS -- WAGES AND 
SALARIES; LOS ANGELES -- SCHOOLS; STRIKES; SETTLEMENTS; LOS ANGELES UNIFIED 
SCHOOL DISTRICT; ASSAULTS -- LOS ANGELES; JOHNSON, WAYNE; BRITTON, LEONARD M; 
UNITED TEACHERS OF LOS ANGELES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052589-0047 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 61563 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
