ZIYANG; DENG XIAOPING; COMMUNIST PARTY (CHINA); CHINA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; 
STUDENTS -- CHINA; DEMONSTRATIONS -- CHINA; CHINA -- ARMED FORCES 
</P>
