<P>
May 25, 1989, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part 2; Page 1; Column 3; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
693 words 
</P>
